product.name: VPS - Build. Set your price and pay!
product.description: Simply tell us what you need, how much you'll pay and then make payment to us. We'll then manually review your offer to us and if we accept your request that is the price you'll pay each time you renew! Simple. All our VPS packages come with the following as standard: KVM virtualization 24/7 Self-service portal to stop/start/reinstall at any time 24/7 Technical assistance Free DDoS Protection (UK only) Fast 1 Gbps Uplink ...and much more! Please be realistic with your request. Terms: payment must be made for us to consider your order. Orders where no payment is made within 6 hours of placement will be rejected without consideration. If we do not accept your offer we will refund your transaction minus any payment processing fees incurred (also applies to the 30 day money-back guarantee for this product). The fairer your offer to us, the more likely it is that we will accept it. We may send you a counter offer. If the price you define is based on a price you'd like us to match from a competitor then raise a ticket to our sales dept. immediately after raising the order with details of the quotation you'd like us to price match. No orders (price match request or otherwise) will be considered unless payment is made in full (to stop timewasters). The minimum price for a VPS is £1.50 per month. If you select neither an IPv4 or an IPv6 address, it will be assumed you want an IPv6 only VPS. Windows OS require at least 20GB storage.
